<h1>Get Started With Cloudflare R2</h1>
<p>Cloudflare R2 is a great performer and cheap alternative to the other major service providers.  It does lack a number of features though, but provides all the basics you need for offloading your media.</p>
<p>Before we configure Media Cloud to work with Cloudflare R2, please watch the tutorial to make sure that you've set everything up correctly on your Cloudflare account.</p>
<p>Once you've done all of that, click on <strong>Next</strong> to configure Media Cloud.</p>
